 in addition to the three hours of his interviews every day?

3:56:28.320 --> 3:56:30.800
 No, not every day, but he listens to a lot of these.

3:56:30.800 --> 3:56:31.640
 I love it.

3:56:31.640 --> 3:56:32.460
 And we talk about it.

3:56:32.460 --> 3:56:33.300
 I love it.

3:56:33.300 --> 3:56:34.140
 We argue about it.

